    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.4L M96 flat-six engine, delivering linear power delivery and that signature boxer acoustic profile. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transaxle offers precise shift gates, complemented by a recent clutch replacement and a dual-row ceramic IMS bearing upgrade for enhanced valvetrain reliability. The chassis retains its communicative feedback through a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, while the four-piston Brembo monobloc calipers provide consistent thermal management during spirited driving. Finished in a classic palette, this car exhibits honest patina consistent with its age but remains mechanically robust with a well-maintained cooling system and optimized fuel injection maps.",
